text: The Alumni Relations is part of the Institutional Advancement Department. Our goal is to facilitate alumni participation, raise funds, strengthen, and extend the College community, and its programs. Alumni Relations is the catalyst to stay in touch with your lifelong community, and find the support you need to innovate, inform, and inspire.

text: The Alumni Association is an independent, incorporated entity established in 1979 with the mission to preserve the value of York College by uplifting its image and visibility through communicating and asserting a working relationship with alumni, administration, faculty, staff, students and surrounding community. Individually, as well as collectively, we maintain that York College remains the beacon on the hill. We commit ourselves to do all that is possible for York College to persevere academically, financially, morally and visibly.
